{"tid":1517511,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(和理非入) 十一月區選必勝法","createTime":"2019-08-30T02:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T02:58:23.000Z","uid":265477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eda45e1f1c9177c98e33e45377575cc81872c2d4","tid":1517511,"uid":265477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:54:28.000Z","msg":"對唔住做咗標題黨<br />\n必勝法係政府講嘅<br />\n<br />\n對於好多和理非嚟講<br />\n佢哋覺得等到十一月<br />\n就可以靠區選大巴大巴咁車埋政府度<br />\n<br />\n我同大家講<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無可能</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n原因好簡單<br />\n<br />\n1. DQ<br />\n2. 種票<br />\n<br />\n最重要係第3點<br />\n到時到候我擺一兩個19生面口話自己係民主同路人落區<br />\n仲要周圍同人講我地兩三個素人打佢一個建制<br />\n形勢大好乜乜七七<br />\n到時仲唔贏到開巷？<br />\n<br />\n和理非咪咁天真<br />\n每個星期做返啲合法嘅實事<br />\n㩒下錢零消費搭多啲公共交通工具睇下樓壓下價咁<br />\n慢慢將呢啲變成生活習慣<br />\n區選到時再諗"},{"pid":"ab5ee116e2fb8241216a794e73a7af48a6efeac4","tid":1517511,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8qooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=3df66b51\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8qooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=54f63efd\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8qooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=a3f6d338\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou